<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Error</title>
    <style>
        body{
            margin: 0px;
            padding: 0px;
            background-color: black;
            font-family: monospace;

            display: grid;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        h1{
            color: white;
            letter-spacing: 0.1in;
            font-size: 40px;
            margin-top: 100px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        hr{
            width: 85vw;
            border: 2px white solid;
        }
        div{
            width: 70vw;
            height: 70vh;

            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            align-content: center;
            justify-items: center;
            gap: 0px 50px;
        }
            p{
                grid-column: 1/2;
                color: aliceblue;
                font-size: 20px;
                line-height: 0.5in;
                width: 42vw;
            }
                a{
                    color: blue;
                    text-decoration: none;
                }
                a:hover{
                    text-decoration: underline;
                }
            img{
                grid-column: 2/3;
                border-radius: 20px;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>
        400 Bad Request
    </h1>
    <hr />
    <div>
        <p>
            Ooops! Your request could not be processed. <a href = '/'>Return home</a> or go back to <a href = '/pokemon/new'>previous page</a> and resubmit form. Check that all input fields are filled out.
        </p>
        <img src = '/images/pokemon-sad.gif'/>
    </div>
</body>
</html>